---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About — Roger Wibrew">
  <main class="container">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      I’m a chemical engineer focused on <strong>process simulation</strong>, <strong>dynamic systems</strong>, and
      <strong>engineering software</strong>. My work connects fundamental modeling (thermodynamics and system dynamics)
      with modern implementation (web apps, automation, and AI-assisted development).
    </p>
    <p>
      This site is a growing portfolio of technical writing and small tools that demonstrate how I approach problems:
      define assumptions clearly, build models that can be tested, and deliver outputs people can actually use.
    </p>
    <p>
      Over time, this website will evolve into a professional services platform as I move into consulting and contract work.
    </p>
  </main>

  <style>
    .container { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 1.25rem; }
    h1 { margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    p { line-height: 1.7; }
  </style>
</Layout>
